cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for inter-sentence relation extraction. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses neural network models, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with graph-based models, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
